{
  "texts": [
    "A detailed quality assessment for each study is presented in Appendix-Table 1.The three included non-RCTs all had moderate risks.",
    "A common serious risk factor among all studies was the consideration of confounders.",
    "None of the study reported potential confounders, which contribute to the potential bias of the study results.",
    "In addition, intervention adherence was a concern in all studies.",
    "Due to the moderate to high dropout rates, the handling of the missing values was problematic in two out of the three studies."
  ]
}